<title>AUSTRALIA: RTRS-Premier bids for Discovery.</title>
<headline>RTRS-Premier bids for Discovery.</headline>
<dateline>SYDNEY 1996-09-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Premier Oil Plc said on Monday it intended to make a takeover offer for all the shares in Discovery Peterolum NL at 70 cents a share.  </p>
<p>The offer values Discovery at about A$91.9 million, assuming purchase of all executive options, Premier said.</p>
<p>&quot;The offer is expected to be conditional on, amongst other things, Premier securing acceptances for at least 50.1 percent of Discovery shares,&quot; Premier said.</p>
<p>Premier said the offer price was higher than Discovery shares had traded at any time in the past two years.</p>
<p>Discovery shares closed at 60 cents on Friday.</p>
